This involves topics related to communication systems (cs.NI), information theory (cs.IT), and electromagnetics (cs.EM). The paper also discusses the impact of the channel on the overall system performance, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper proposes methods to optimize the channel, which involves engineering and design aspects (cs.AR).
